Zend Server/CE Cache Adapter for Joomla! 1.5
--------------------------------------------


INSTALLATION
------------

In order to use this adapter you have to run Joomla! 1.5 using Zend Server.
You can download the Community Edition of Zend Server for free from this website:
http://www.zend.com/en/products/server-ce/downloads

To install the Zend Server Cache adapter for Joomla! 1.5 copy all the *.php files of the zip package in the joomla folder: libraries/joomla/cache/storage/

After that you can choose the cache handler Zendserver_disk and Zendserver_shm from the System tab of the Global Configuration menu of the Administration interface of Joomla.



